    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《东方恋迷踪: 妖怪传说与幻想之旅》是<i>东方Project</i>二次创作作品，是一款以「骰子」为战斗核心的策略冒险RPG。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>交流QQ主群：776381042</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Discord：GY4chsGpuW</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609270/extras/1351e4f2e152d9ccc75ee3df9ad41c29.poster.avif?t=1771415646\" width=455 height=241 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609270/extras/1351e4f2e152d9ccc75ee3df9ad41c29.webm?t=1771415646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>游戏拥有<strong>7个章节丰富跌宕的剧情、充实且重复性低的收集要素、灵活自由的道中体验、新颖但折磨人的BOSS机制</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏操作简单易上手，只需鼠标即可游玩，拥有<strong>3种难度模式</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一种满足<strong>「策略玩家」</strong>的回合计算规划；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一种满足<strong>「动作玩家」</strong>的即时战斗操作；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还有一种完全跳过战斗，满足<strong>「手残/剧情玩家」</strong>的完整流程体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏剧情和氛围轻松、欢乐、愉快，可以在茶余饭后休闲游玩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609270/extras/6b7c58de0202334d002f503ee4fa152e.avif?t=1771415646\" width=600 height=337 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【故事梗概】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >某一日，恋听姐姐说有一篇可以置人于死地的诅咒之诗的存在。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >于是她与姐姐打赌谁先揭开传说。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从地灵殿出发，漫步幻想乡全境，搜集线索，并帮助妖怪们解决沿途的传说。最终揭开一切的真相，并回到地灵殿履行与姐姐的约定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >旅程将途经间歇泉、玄武之泽、妖怪山、红魔馆、魔法森林、人间之里、三途河、旧地狱等多个地区。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遭遇各式各样的怪奇传说，也会遭遇超过40名妖怪和妖精角色，其中有阻挠你前行的宿敌，也有助你一臂之力的友人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【本作特色】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◆最简洁的系统，最低的上手门槛，衍生出不失深度的游戏性</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在经典的「日式RPG」的基础上进行了大规模轻量化设计。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有「经验值」和「等级」系统，不需要刷级。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有需要跑的关卡小地图，一切移动均在幻想乡的「大地图」，以及花样连接的随机要素(Rouge)「地下城」。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609270/extras/c2b85e1593925510fe27a4d61b98b28e.avif?t=1771415646\" width=600 height=336 /></span>战斗全部1V1公平对决，一回合内鼠标无需点击第二下。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609270/extras/f8c2e988a6296d99f0910761e5d36d9f.avif?t=1771415646\" width=600 height=290 /></span>随时随地「即时自动存档」，无需手动保存，每走一步都将保存你的进度，杜绝丢档麻烦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「战败也能无损回到战败之前」，没有任何负面惩罚，反而可能推动剧情进展。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609270/extras/e51b713369171bf39271163349a3b997.avif?t=1771415646\" width=600 height=336 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但是</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◆潜在的难度，可能对错误估算自己实力的玩家，产生卡关的阻碍</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中无论你选择哪个模式进行游玩，敌人的强度和招数配置都是相同的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BOSS可能不遵守回合规则，即时地对你发动进攻。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609270/extras/7ad3e6e170172000199119706faca1aa.avif?t=1771415646\" width=600 height=336 /></span>强大的敌人，可能使用正常规则下无法招架的技能，对你发起命中即死亡的危险攻击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果不能够见招拆招，可能在生与死之间无限循环。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以在战斗的大部分时机，使用手上的各色武器，接住敌人的攻击、化解敌人的伤害、反发回敌人身上。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609270/extras/98f2b19b14d602bae98518e17414347b.avif?t=1771415646\" width=600 height=336 /></span>敌人会使用东方Project特色且招牌的华丽弹幕，毫不讲理地对你发起命中即死亡的攻击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609270/extras/f0ae99c656117235f3e0ab8a0d27533f.poster.avif?t=1771415646\" width=455 height=241 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609270/extras/f0ae99c656117235f3e0ab8a0d27533f.webm?t=1771415646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>而你也可以使用鼠标和键盘灵活规避弹幕，使用弹幕战正确的应对方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遵守符卡规则的你，在不受伤且成功击破BOSS的符卡时，也会获得收取符卡的奖励。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609270/extras/8d66055e02915605d899b7731bb4f0f4.avif?t=1771415646\" width=600 height=336 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◆众多丰富的收集要素，供深度玩家享受</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各式各样的「统计数据」，将详尽记录你这场史诗级冒险的一点一滴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609270/extras/79efec219661121e057b67da83843472.avif?t=1771415646\" width=600 height=336 /></span>数量繁多的可收集CG，可以在「CG图鉴」确认。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609270/extras/5211be090be8aaea35408ec0c7bcb5de.avif?t=1771415646\" width=600 height=336 /></span>数量繁多的可收集音乐，可以在「音乐图鉴」确认。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609270/extras/6e26d51d0dca9edefb411817c3a6b2fa.avif?t=1771415646\" width=600 height=336 /></span>数量繁多的可收集道具，可以在「遗物图鉴」确认。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个道具均拥有属于自己的故事，帮助你更好的了解东方Project的世界观。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609270/extras/336c010ccd14ce626cc54bc0aed01af8.avif?t=1771415646\" width=600 height=336 /></span>数量繁多的敌人和BOSS，可以在「怪物图鉴」确认。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每位敌人击杀一定数量后，将解锁属于这位妖怪的独特信息，可能埋藏着各种不为人知的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609270/extras/6593186b0d934c838090742cb289ef18.avif?t=1771415646\" width=600 height=336 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◆完善还原的幻想乡地图，个性丰富的角色，跌宕起伏的剧情</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏还原了幻想乡的全景地图，将在这座舞台上展开全新的冒险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以去幻想乡的各处，结识不同的朋友，挑战不同的对手，触发不同的剧情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609270/extras/3d2dee0705ac07c700ad223d29ab04b3.avif?t=1771415646\" width=600 height=336 /></span>作为东方Project的同人游戏，本作有大约40名敌我角色及原创角色登场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还有诸多碍于经费不能露面的角色，会存在于文本介绍和背景板中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >个性丰富能力各异的众多角色，或是成为可靠的同伴，或是成为棘手的强敌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >书写属于你自己的冒险，在冒险途中认识他们，并展开你独一无二的旅程吧。</p>",
